title: Tears Galore (Plastic Cup Boys and Michael Ealy Interview)
itunes:title: Tears Galore (Plastic Cup Boys and Michael Ealy Interview)
description:
Today on the show we had the Plastic Cup Boys Will Spank Horton and Na'im Lynn where they spoke about New Special And Docu-series, Na'im's Acne, Katt Williams, Kevin Hart + More. Also Charlamagne, gave “Donkey of the Day” to a UK Couple Sues Fertility Clinic After Giving Birth To Black Baby Due To Embryo Mix Up. Also, we had Michael Ealy stop by and he spoke about his  New Movie 'The Intruder', Evil Roles In Film, Independent Productions and More.
